{"tid":1210471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警察速入] 知唔知點死都唔用警車擋路要用你地做人盾？","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T13:53:55.000Z","uid":72652,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e6450317dba7c73290580c0781946b4fa751b462","tid":1210471,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:50:55.000Z","msg":"因為部車值錢過你地條人命呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個政府唔值得你地為佢賣命<br />\n<br />\n問心<br />\n你想唔想下一代的香港變到好似而加的中國咁？<br />\n<br />\n工可以照返<br />\n慶祝相可以照影<br />\n<br />\n但下次開槍 揮警棍個陣<br />\n做個樣就得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你老細係唔會因爲你扑濕多幾個示威者而升你職<br />\n<br />\n反之比網民點左相<br />\n起你底 <br />\n你的黑材料就從此流傳落去<br />\n<br />\n用下你個腦諗下<br />\n你為份糧姐<br />\n無謂要自己惹禍上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n槍口一致向中共同淋病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a4dfcfa1e486391063b6cc366c9805b952a6f3","tid":1210471,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}